---
title: Beefed-Up Bolognese with Poblano Peppers and Thyme
description: Some bolognese recipes call for hours of slow stovetop simmering, but this recipe isn't like other recipes, not by a long shot. We're not only speeding up the path towards beefy, pasta-filled bliss, but also inviting a few new friends along for the ride. Sweet poblano peppers, tender carrots, and even a dollop of sour cream join in on the fun to give this dish a Tex-Mex-inspired twist.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smoky-poblano-bolognese-w01-bdb44a19.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/smoky-poblano-bolognese-w01-63571a79.pdf
